<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Thelemic_references">Thelemic references</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sefer_Yetzirah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Thelemic references"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p><a href="/wiki/Charles_Stansfeld_Jones" title="Charles Stansfeld Jones">Charles Stansfeld Jones</a>, in his book called <i>The Anatomy of The Body of God</i><sup id="cite_ref-24" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-24">&#91;24&#93;</a></sup> has written interpretations of this book in <a href="/wiki/Thelema" title="Thelema">Thelema</a>.
</p>
